-- Diamond Foods Names New CEO, CFO
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2012-02-08T21:24:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-08/diamond-foods-names-new-ceo-cfo.html
Diamond Foods Inc. (DMND)  said it appointed
a new chief executive officer and chief financial officer after
its  audit committee  discovered that results for 2010 and 2011
will need to be restated over the accounting for payments made
to walnut growers.  Rick Wolford, a Diamond Foods director and former Del Monte
Foods CEO, was named acting chief executive, and Michael Murphy
of Alix Partners was named acting financial chief. Michael J.
Mendes and Steven M. Neil were placed on administrative leave.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  